# Figma to Flutter (project rule)

- For any task mentioning Figma, follow the **Figma-to-Flutter** skill workflow (`.cursor/skills/figma-to-flutter/SKILL.md`).
- This repository targets Flutter. Never leave final output as web, React, Tailwind, HTML, or CSS.
- Reuse existing theme, tokens, and shared widgets wherever possible.
- Avoid hardcoded colors, typography, spacing, radii, and shadows when the project has theme or token equivalents.
- Validate visually against the Figma screenshot before considering the task complete **if** a Figma screenshot is available through MCP or the skill workflow. Ignore this requirement when no such screenshot is available.
